data.description: Buyer is offering a $1000 credit for closing cost and/or points with an acceptable offer!  First Day of Show is Nov 1 so please ignore the days on market.  Beautiful home ready for immediate occupancy.  Get in before the holidays.  In very nice condition and move in ready.  Neutral wall and floors.  Come look for yourself.  Home has a beautiful kitchen with breakfast/dining combo.  Nice large great room with fireplace and vaulted ceilings.  Seperate floor plan, walk  out with finished lower level and full bedroom and bathroom.  MFL. Beautiful custom cabinets and granite counter top with a stone base.  Large backyard, partial fencing and beautiful deck with stairs to lower level.  Great school district close to subdivision.  4 bedrooms and 3 full baths in this lovely ranch maintenance free home.  Plenty of storage area too.
